timing_set_sca...egative_checks(25.10)  timing_set_sca...egative_checks(25.10)

Name
       timing_set_scaling_for_negative_checks

Syntax
        timing_set_scaling_for_negative_checks

       {default | divider | multiplier}

       Default: default

       When  set  to default, the derated check is the negative check * (2.0 -
       derating factor), where the derating factor is the value that  you  set
       using the set_timing_derate command.

       Modifies  the scaling of the negative timing analysis check value. This
       variable does not affect the positive checks. When set to divider,  di-
       vides the negative check value by the derating factor. When set to mul-
       tiplier, multiplies the negative check value by the derating factor.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

